The paper proposes a method to accelerate the inference procedure of deep Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) by pruning filters. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), as well as artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language processing (NLP) datasets, indicating a possible connection to computational linguistics (cs.CL).
